scopecontent.p:
The numerous receipts in the collection include receipts
         from: the 
         Richmond Enquirer; 
         J. Reynolds, the local minister; 
         Rich Branton, the boot maker; postal
         expenses; 
         Joseph Williamsand 
         John Collins, day laborers; 
         David Lipscomb, stabler; and 
         Joseph Adams, the Lewis family tutor.
